Util

Class ProjectPaths

  • java.lang.Object
    • Util.ProjectPaths

  • public final class ProjectPaths
extends Object
    The ProjectPaths class provides helper functions for accessing the file system of the project and fetching buggy and fixed Defects4J patches.

                                        ArrayList<com.github.javaparser.ast.CompilationUnit> patches)
                                 throws Exception
        Copies a set of patches to the /output/ folder.
        Parameters:
        identifier - Defects4j project file name e.g. Lang or Closure
        bid - Unique id of the Defects4j bug
        mutationOperatorName - The name of the mutation operator that was used to create the patch

        Throws:
        Exception - If the patch cannot be copied to the /output directory
